 a\, there's nothing better you can do for yourself than to build your own 
 little sprocket bot. In this workshop\, learn how you can build that bot t
 hrough command line tools (makefile\, node.js\, python) to automate tasks 
 like mapmaking. Learn workflow tips for Illustrator\, Photoshop\, Blender\
 , and more! Save time by setting up a file and forever more executing it v
 ia a push of the button.\nFolks with an understanding of command line tool
