BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:[Demo] Cheatsheet: An investigative spreadsheet tool powered by A.
 I.
DTSTART;TZID=EST;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260306T154500
DTEND;TZID=EST;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260306T164500
UID:nicar-2026-1147@ire.org
DESCRIPTION:In this session\, we will demo Cheatsheet\, an internal tool d
 eveloped at The New York Times that has helped in the reporting process fo
 r dozens of breaking news and investigative stories.\nCheatsheet is a smar
 t spreadsheet application that makes it quick and easy to analyze large da
 tasets\, document dumps and media collections at scale using A.I. systems.
  Cheatsheet gives reporters the ability to quickly find needles in large h
 aystacks using recipes such as A.I. classification\, translation\, summari
 zation\, quote extraction and web search.\n\nAI | Skill: Intermediate
