UID:nicar-2026-1154@ire.org
DESCRIPTION:NO RECORDING! Covering sensitive topics can take an emotional 
 toll\, including long working hours\, emotional strain and personal sacrif
 ices. A panel of journalists will share strategies that help attendees rec
 ognize early signs of stress\, create grounding techniques and find health
 y outlets outside of work to protect their mental health.\n\nCareer | Skil
 l: Beginner
