BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:[Panel] Persuasion 401: The psychology of investigative reporting
DTSTART;TZID=EST;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260306T101500
DTEND;TZID=EST;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260306T111500
UID:nicar-2026-1157@ire.org
DESCRIPTION:This training provides a deep dive into the psychology of pers
 uasion so that reporters can increase their odds in getting record custodi
 ans to cough up data\, reluctant sources to talk\, and editors to support 
 their projects. Tips will be research-based and help attendees learn the p
 ower of the mind. Note: Use these strategies for good\, not evil!\n\nPubli
 c records | Skill: Beginner
LOCATION:White River G
URL:https://schedules.ire.org/nicar-2026#session-1157
