SUMMARY:[Panel] How to find data
DTSTART;TZID=EST;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260306T101500
DTEND;TZID=EST;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260306T111500
UID:nicar-2026-1204@ire.org
DESCRIPTION:A conversation about how to find and vet credible data sources
  that you can use right away.\n\nStory ideas\, Public records\, Local\, Be
 at reporting | Skill: Beginner
LOCATION:White River B
URL:https://schedules.ire.org/nicar-2026#session-1204
X-SOURCE:NICAR 2026
END:VEVENT
