DTEND;TZID=EDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260308T123000
UID:nicar-2026-1208@ire.org
DESCRIPTION:You've picked up some new skills\, filled your brain with insp
 iration and your notebook with ideas\, but now what? We'll give you some t
 ips on how to take advantage of what you've learned\, avoid letting your s
 kills get rusty and even continue learning when you get back to your job. 
 Bring your questions\, too! We'll have lots of time for that.\n\nCareer\, 
 Story ideas\, Students | Skill: Beginner
LOCATION:White River B
URL:https://schedules.ire.org/nicar-2026#session-1208
X-SOURCE:NICAR 2026
