BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:[Panel] How to avoid a midterm meltdown: Tips for covering electio
 ns
DTSTART;TZID=EST;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260307T113000
DTEND;TZID=EST;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260307T123000
UID:nicar-2026-1215@ire.org
DESCRIPTION:This panel will show how journalists navigate covering electio
 ns with data and how to avoid common mistakes. Speakers will share tips an
 d stories about reporting on election results\, campaign finance\, and vot
 er turnout.\n\nBeat reporting\, Story ideas | Skill: Beginner
LOCATION:White River B
URL:https://schedules.ire.org/nicar-2026#session-1215
