DTSTART;TZID=EST;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260307T170000
DTEND;TZID=EST;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260307T180000
UID:nicar-2026-1237@ire.org
DESCRIPTION:Need help on a data project? Having trouble figuring out how t
 o use that cool tool you learned about in another session? Just want to ne
 twork with some other news nerds? Stop by this session and get one-on-one 
 help from experienced data journalists who would be delighted to help you 
 solve your problems.\n\nData analysis | Skill: Beginner
