BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:[Hands-on] Google Sheets 2: Formulas & sorting
DTSTART;TZID=EST;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260305T101500
DTEND;TZID=EST;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260305T111500
UID:nicar-2026-1257@ire.org
DESCRIPTION:Much of Google Sheets' power comes in the form of formulas. In
  this class\, you'll learn how to use them to analyze data with the eye of
  a journalist. Yes\, math will be involved\, but it's totally worth it! Th
 is class will show you how calculations like change\, percent change\, rat
 es and ratios can beef up your reporting.\nThis session is good for: Anyon
 e who has taken Google Sheets 1 or has been introduced to spreadsheets. At
 tendees will need to bring their own laptop (no tablets) for the training 
 and will need a free Google account to participate.\n\nData analysis | Ski
 ll: Beginner
LOCATION:202
URL:https://schedules.ire.org/nicar-2026#session-1257
X-SOURCE:NICAR 2026
END:VEVENT
