DTEND;TZID=EST;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260305T123000
UID:nicar-2026-1258@ire.org
DESCRIPTION:A look at the awesome power of pivot — and how to use it to 
 analyze your dataset in minutes rather than hours. We'll work up to using 
