BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:[Hands-on] Introduction to R
DTSTART;TZID=EST;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260307T090000
DTEND;TZID=EST;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260307T123000
UID:nicar-2026-1278@ire.org
DESCRIPTION:We'll introduce you to R\, a free\, powerful open-source progr
 amming language that will take your data reporting to the next level. By t
 he end of this three-hour session\, you will be able to read data from com
 mon file types into R\, clean and explore it\, create visualizations\, and
  make your entire data workflow reproducible. We'll also talk about how to
  find help when you're stuck.\nWorkshop prerequisites: This session will b
 e most helpful if you’re comfortable working with data and you’re read
 y to take your skills to the next level.\nPreregistration is required and 
 seating is limited. Laptops will be provided for the training.\n\nData ana
 lysis | Skill: Intermediate
LOCATION:204
URL:https://schedules.ire.org/nicar-2026#session-1278
X-SOURCE:NICAR 2026
