DTSTART;TZID=EST;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260306T113000
DTEND;TZID=EST;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260306T123000
UID:nicar-2026-1279@ire.org
DESCRIPTION:Leading investigative journalists can be extra challenging\, s
 o let us help! Socialize\, forge partnerships or find a support group at t
 his NICAR26 meetup! Swap best practices\, laugh at lessons learned along y
 our journey and find out more about IRE’s upcoming management training i
 nitiatives!\nThis networking event takes place directly after the always-p
 opular\, slightly shorter\, FREE “Managing Investigators” master class
 . You don’t have to attend the master class in order to stop by the meet
 up\, though we welcome you to check it out! This networking session is for
  anyone managing (or aspiring to manage) investigators.\n\nEvent\, Managem
 ent | Skill: Beginner
LOCATION:209
