UID:nicar-2026-1281@ire.org
DESCRIPTION:Level up your reporting with Gemini. This session focuses on k
 ey features like Deep Research for multi-step investigations\, Custom Gems
  for scalable tasks\, and Canvas for interactive drafting. Plus\, discover
