BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:[Hands-on] Navigating federal campaign finance data
DTSTART;TZID=EDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260308T101500
DTEND;TZID=EDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260308T111500
UID:nicar-2026-1282@ire.org
DESCRIPTION:This class will focus on using the FEC’s web tools to access
  data. It will feature a hands-on demonstration of accessing reports as so
 on as they are filed. Participants will learn what is included in the repo
 rts\, how to interpret entries\, and potential pitfalls. The presenter wil
 l share a user-friendly spreadsheet template for viewing downloaded report
  data and walk participants through a simple recipe for creating compellin
 g stories using campaign finance data.\nThis session is good for everyone.
  Laptops will be provided.\n\nElections | Skill: Beginner
LOCATION:202
URL:https://schedules.ire.org/nicar-2026#session-1282
