DTSTART;TZID=EST;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260305T113000
DTEND;TZID=EST;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260305T123000
UID:nicar-2026-1285@ire.org
DESCRIPTION:Mix and mingle\, meet friends old and new\, and build your pro
 fessional community in this fun and informal networking session.\nThis ses
 sion is for journalism students.\n\nStudents | Skill: Beginner
LOCATION:White River B
URL:https://schedules.ire.org/nicar-2026#session-1285
X-SOURCE:NICAR 2026
