UID:nicar-2026-1291@ire.org
DESCRIPTION:Mix and mingle\, meet friends old and new\, and build your pro
 fessional community in this fun and informal networking session.\nThis ses
 sion is for anyone who identifies as part of the LGBTQIA+ community or as 
 an ally.\n\nEvent | Skill: Beginner
LOCATION:White River I
