DTSTART;TZID=EST;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260307T170000
DTEND;TZID=EST;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260307T180000
UID:nicar-2026-1292@ire.org
DESCRIPTION:Transform your reporting workflow with NotebookLM\, your perso
 nal AI research assistant. We will cover how to instantly synthesize compl
 ex beats\, generate inline citations\, and explore features like audio ove
 rviews\, mind maps\, and data extraction—all while keeping your material
 s organized and searchable.\n\nAI | Skill: Intermediate
