SUMMARY:[Hands-on] Finding the story: Education data
DTSTART;TZID=EST;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260305T101500
DTEND;TZID=EST;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260305T111500
UID:nicar-2026-1294@ire.org
DESCRIPTION:The issues we cover in education reporting are wide-ranging 
 – from who manages our education institutions\, to how students perform\
 , to how colleges are funded. Let’s go over some ways to set yourself up
  for success as an education data reporter by learning about helpful datas
 ets\, how to request and organize information\, and how to avoid common pi
 tfalls when working on an education team.\nThis session is good for anyone
 ! You must bring your own laptop (no tablets) to participate.\n\nBeat repo
 rting | Skill: Beginner
