BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:[Hands-on] Finding the story:  Data to decode deportation
DTSTART;TZID=EST;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260306T113000
DTEND;TZID=EST;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260306T123000
UID:nicar-2026-1296@ire.org
DESCRIPTION:In this session\, we will walk through some stories published 
 by The Minnesota Star Tribune during ICE's unprecedented immigration crack
 down and share some tips\, data and resources for preparing timely data an
 alysis of federal deportation activities in your state. This session is go
 od for beginners. Attendees will need to bring their own laptop (no tablet
 s) to participate in this class.\n\nStory ideas\, Data analysis | Skill: B
 eginner
LOCATION:102
URL:https://schedules.ire.org/nicar-2026#session-1296
X-SOURCE:NICAR 2026
