DTSTART;TZID=EST;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260307T101500
DTEND;TZID=EST;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260307T111500
UID:nicar-2026-1301@ire.org
DESCRIPTION:In this session\, women\, trans and non-binary folks in data j
 ournalism and investigative reporting will discuss the unique challenges t
 hey face\, including the nuances of working in the field\, issues of impos
 ter syndrome and how to be our own advocates. Participants will have a saf
 e space to ask questions\, share experiences and network with one another.
 \n\nEvent | Skill: Beginner
LOCATION:White River G
URL:https://schedules.ire.org/nicar-2026#session-1301
X-SOURCE:NICAR 2026
