UID:nicar-2026-1335@ire.org
DESCRIPTION:Data-driven investigations don’t have to be long projects. I
 n this panel\, journalism educators will break down student data stories y
 ou can replicate in your own classroom or community. We’ll cover the dat
 a\, the process and what can go wrong.\n\nStudents\, Story ideas | Skill: 
 Beginner
