SUMMARY:[Demo] Pitch\, please! How to contribute to the IRE Journal
DTSTART;TZID=EST;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260305T143000
DTEND;TZID=EST;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260305T180000
UID:nicar-2026-1336@ire.org
DESCRIPTION:Do you have a cool data project you want to highlight? Some FO
 IA expertise you wanna share? How about some *thoughts* about the industry
 ? Pitch IRE Journal managing editor Adam Rhodes in the exhibitor hall!\n\n
 Story ideas | Skill: Beginner
