SUMMARY:[Hands-on] From good to great data viz design
DTSTART;TZID=EST;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260305T113000
DTEND;TZID=EST;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260305T123000
UID:nicar-2026-1347@ire.org
DESCRIPTION:Learn design tips for polishing your graphics to tell clear an
 d compelling stories. This tool-agnostic session will involve participator
 y discussion where we review example charts and maps as a group\, covering
  design challenges like focusing the user’s attention\, making complex d
 ata understandable\, and using non-standard chart types. Feel free to brin
 g one of your own graphics to workshop with the group.\nThis session is go
 od for: People who create graphics and are interested in learning how to i
 mprove their design.\n\nData viz | Skill: Beginner
LOCATION:201
URL:https://schedules.ire.org/nicar-2026#session-1347
X-SOURCE:NICAR 2026
