UID:nicar-2026-1352@ire.org
DESCRIPTION:A look at the awesome power of pivot — and how to use it to 
 analyze your dataset in minutes rather than hours. We'll work up to using 
 a pivot table by first sorting and filtering a dataset\, learning how to f
 ind story ideas along the way.\nThis class will be taught on Mac computers
 .\nThis session is good for: Anyone familiar with formulas\, sorting and f
 iltering in Excel or another spreadsheet program. Laptops will be provided
 .\n\nData analysis | Skill: Beginner
LOCATION:205
