DESCRIPTION:Are you a member of one of IRE's new student chapters? Interes
 ted in starting one on your campus? Or just want to find other students to
  hang with during lunch?\nGrab your lunch and bring it with you to our stu
 dent chapter meetup!\nMembers from IRE's student chapters will share ideas
