UID:nicar-2026-1361@ire.org
DESCRIPTION:What networking isn't: Collecting business cards and letting t
 hem gather dust in your desk drawer. What netowrking is: A way to build tw
 o-way relationships that turn into long-term connections. This workshop of
 fers tips on creating the perfect elevator pitch to introduce yourself\, f
 inding the right people to meet and starting to build mutually beneficial 
 conversations that translate into opportunities\, collaborators and purpos
 eful long-term connections.\n\nCareer
